Install the ARM cross-compiler and QEMU:
bashsudo apt install gcc-arm-linux-gnueabihf qemu-user
Then compile and run:
bash# Cross-compile for ARM
arm-linux-gnueabihf-gcc assessment.s -o assessment -nostdlib -static

# Run with QEMU
qemu-arm ./assessment


Option 3: Use an online ARM emulator

CPUlator — ARM simulator in browser
VisUAL — ARM emulator for learning